cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV. 

This paper is about natural language processing, specifically dependency parsing. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category. The paper also introduces a novel transition system, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also discusses the performance of the parser, which suggests that it may fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) categories.
